  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
    <subfield code="m">The answer to this question may one day be of practical importance: In order to save construction materials, one would like to build the confining mirror as close as possible to the black-hole horizon</subfield>
    <subfield code="o">44</subfield>
